WEBVTT

00:08.026 --> 00:09.948
♪ It's astounding ♪

00:10.164 --> 00:12.164
♪ Time is fleeting

00:12.930 --> 00:15.381
♪ Madness

00:15.383 --> 00:18.718
♪ Takes its toll

00:18.720 --> 00:21.003
♪ But listen closely

00:21.005 --> 00:23.873
♪ Not for very much longer

00:23.875 --> 00:29.312
♪ I've got to keep control ♪

00:29.897 --> 00:32.281
♪ I remember

00:32.284 --> 00:35.618
♪ Doing the time warp

00:35.620 --> 00:37.186
♪ Drinking

00:37.188 --> 00:40.290
♪ Those moments when

00:40.292 --> 00:42.792
♪ The blackness hit me

00:42.794 --> 00:46.079
♪ And the void
would be calling ♪

00:46.081 --> 00:51.551
♪ <i>Let's do the time warp again</i> ♪

00:51.553 --> 00:56.706
♪ <i>Let's do</i>
<i>the time warp again</i> ♪

00:56.708 --> 00:59.709
♪ It's just a jump
to the left... ♪

00:59.711 --> 01:01.895
(growling)

01:05.149 --> 01:07.183
What the hell?
Watch out, man.

01:07.185 --> 01:08.151
Chill out, buddy.

01:08.153 --> 01:09.903
What the hell is wrong
with this guy?

01:09.905 --> 01:11.738
Somebody get the police.

01:11.740 --> 01:12.888
Sabrina, stay here.

01:12.890 --> 01:14.056
WOMAN:
Who is this guy?

01:14.058 --> 01:16.326
Uh, sir?

01:16.328 --> 01:18.278
I'm a doctor.

01:18.280 --> 01:19.412
Are you all right?

01:19.414 --> 01:20.580
Sir.

01:20.582 --> 01:21.681
Max!

01:21.683 --> 01:22.749
Oh, my gosh,
are you okay?

01:22.751 --> 01:23.700
What's your problem, man?

01:23.702 --> 01:26.402
(men grunting)

01:26.404 --> 01:27.370
(yells)

01:27.372 --> 01:29.122
Get off! Get off!

01:29.124 --> 01:30.256
Hey, hey, hey!
You see that guy?

01:30.258 --> 01:31.758
(partygoers clamoring)

01:31.760 --> 01:33.960
Now, sir, back off! Come on!

01:33.962 --> 01:35.378
I said back off!

01:35.380 --> 01:37.460
(partygoers yelling, screaming)
He just bit that guy.

01:43.721 --> 01:44.771
(gunshot)

01:44.773 --> 01:46.439
(woman screams)

01:46.441 --> 01:48.691
(grunting)

01:48.693 --> 01:52.278
<i>(Hawaii Five-O</i>
theme song plays)

01:52.303 --> 01:56.303
<font color="#00FF00">♪ Hawaii Five-O 4x06 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF"Kupouli 'la (Broken)</font>
